      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/40/764",
      "text": [
        " اَلْقِبْلَةِ قَالَ «لاَ يَصْلُحُ لَهُ أَنْ يَسْتَقْبِلَ اَلنَّارَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.764 - He (Ali ibn Ja'far) asked about whether it is permissible for a man to pray with a lamp (or flame) placed in front of him in the direction of the Qibla.\nImam (as) said: \"It is not permissible for him to face the fire.\""
        ]
      }
    },
